opera: Opera - Small, fast, and secure Web browser
opera:
opera: Opera is a powerful tool that gives you more options when surfing the
opera: Web.  It is faster, safer, and easier to use than most other Web
opera: browsers.  Opera is actually a suite of programs which includes the
opera: Web browser itself, plus a mail/news/RSS reader, an IRC chat client,
opera: and a BitTorrent client.  It has a multitude of advanced features.
opera: Now Opera comes with Fraud Protection, which is off by default.
opera: NOTE: This is an international package build.
opera:
opera: Packaged by Georgi D. Sotirov <gdsotirov@dir.bg>
